{"tid":1634503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔做勇武了，返去唱歌","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:08:24.000Z","uid":231905,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"264c1f59b697db0844c31a9d27596824ac3af46c","tid":1634503,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：上次發夢衝最前，帶住一班手足上</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">敵人反對就支持，敵人支持就反對</span>，唔記得左毛主席智慧？<br />\n封鐵，唔出不反，極早出TG，都係想冇人再遊行，無法表達訴求。<br />\n點解派臥底燒野放火？就係嫌你唔夠激。<br />\n<br />\n裝修燒野對國際戰線有咩影響好多巴絲分析過，我唔係咩高人，我唔分析。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我好簡單，林奠想我做乜，我就掉轉做</span></span>，根本都唔洗諗咁多。<br />\n<br />\n今晚唱歌歌，玩面具人鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0a0f341d532cdc5e51a1ea1d99c2674d1a78a4","tid":1634503,"uid":126062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日十月二 全民三罷 全港繼續死城 </strong></span></span><br />\n有冇人跟！！有既急需文宣！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5a7881e16c4f2c94df4eaba1bfde189c32b740fd","tid":1634503,"uid":231905,"like":6,